\frac{d^2y}{dt^2} + \frac{9\mu}{2\rho_s a^2}\frac{dy}{dt} + \frac{k}{m_{eff}}y + \frac{9\mu}{2a^2\rho_s\sqrt{\pi}}\int_0^t \frac{d^2y/d\tau^2}{\sqrt{t-\tau}}d\tau = -\frac{3\rho_f V_0\omega\cos(\omega t)}{2\rho_s a}

\frac{d^2z}{dt^2} + \frac{9\mu}{2\rho_s a^2}\frac{dz}{dt} + \frac{k}{m_{eff}}z + \frac{9\mu}{2a^2\rho_s\sqrt{\pi}}\int_0^t \frac{d^2z/d\tau^2}{\sqrt{t-\tau}}d\tau = 0

where m_{eff} = m + \frac{2\pi a^3\rho_f}{3} and \rho_s = \frac{3m}{4\pi a^3}

Parametric resonance condition: \omega = 2\sqrt{\frac{k}{m_{eff}}}

